
-----------
JWRITE HELP
-----------

Options:
  -a|--all         - Compile for all formats
     --bbcode      - Compile for BBCode
  -c|--compile     - Compile the input
  -d|--debug       - Display debugging information
     --epub        - Compile for Epub
  -f|--file        - Specify the output file name for the finished compilation
  -F|--force       - Ignore any warnings
  -h|--help        - Display this help screen
     --html        - Compile for HTML
  -i|--input       - Set the input directory
  -I|--interactive - Require user input to proceed
     --mobi        - Compile for Mobi
  -o|--output      - Set the output directory
     --pdf         - Compile for PDF
     --reset       - Reset jwrite to defaults
     --tex         - Compile for tex (Uses XeLaTeX by default)
     --txt         - Compile for plain text
  -v|--verbose     - Output compilation information to the screen
  -V|--version     - Show version details

